          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": " Patient âgé de 18 ans et plus - Patient atteint de PTI persistant (qui couvre une période comprise entre 3 et 12 mois après le diagnostic) ou chronique (PTI ayant plus de 12 mois d’évolution) selon la définition des recommandations de la HAS. - traité par agonistes TPO-R"
          },
          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Each participating physician is to include in a cross-sectional registry the first patients who are managed for their ITP persistent or chronic. Each physician could fill information about 15 patients maximum.  Among the maximum of 15 patients included in the cross-sectional registry, each participating physician is to include in the cohort, in a consecutive manner, the first 3 to 8 patients with chronic ITP at TPO-R agonist treatment initiation in compliance with the inclusion criteria"
          },
